self,\n", "        n_features,\n", "        n_classes,\n", "        n_hidden_units,\n", "        mc_dropout_p=0.5,\n", "        n_mc_samples=0,\n", "    ):\n", "        super().__init__()\n", " "\n", "        keep_prob = 1.0 - self.mc_dropout_p\n", "        mask = torch.empty(\n", "            *expected_shape,\n", "            device=device,\n", "        ).bernoulli_(keep_prob) /     dropout on the input embeddings.\n", "\n", "        Evaluation mode, MC enabled\n", "            logits_mean : torch.Tensor of shape (n_samples, n_classes)\n", "                Mean logits over MC
